text: Management & staff are all very knowledgable and warm. The site was always well lite and fully secured. I slept well with Public Storage. Public Storage for years has and is my first go to storage. Now living in Macon and waiting for Public to have a few out here as well. You guys must expand out more. Public Storage is a reliable source with committed customers like myself. Thanks guys..soooo very much.
